ps", "resolution": "1080x1920", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/95.0.4638.69 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "format_id": "9", "format": "9 - 1080x1920"}], "title": "Video by memory.lane.project", "description": "They call it the Millennial Ache. We are the last generation that remembers life before the internet, before social media, before life became so loud and fast. We had a foot in both worlds—the analog and the digital. There is something so bittersweet about seeing these grainy videos and remembering how simple life was back then.  I’m making it my mission to bring these memories into the light before they’re gone for good. Thank you all for coming along for the ride! ❤️✨\n#memorylaneproject #MillennialAche #80sBaby #90sNostalgia #HomeMovies", "duration": 60.279, "timestamp": 1767671115, "uploader_id": "77481642439", "uploader": "The Memory Lane Project", "channel": "memory.lane.project", "like_count": 61188, "comment_count": 1572, "comments": [{"author": "darkstar_whitelight", "author_id": "12116858406", "id": "17905305942220373", "text": "😔", "timestamp": 1775354951}, {"author": "tamilnn54", "author_id": "60384872731", "id": "18099428710790187", "text": "1969", "timestamp": 1775354766}, {"author": "louiboi0000", "author_id": "79009002049", "id": "18052282409707837", "text": "Even the McDonalds, pizza huts , Taco Bell’s , Burger King’s had style colors and was made for families now they are dark and screens..", "timestamp": 1775353094}, {"author": "mimitul", "author_id": "258284986", "id": "18062465393681968", "text": "💯😢", "timestamp": 1775347686}, {"author": "junkieinmytrunk", "author_id": "3508237087", "id": "18100908613779158", "text": "The fact this gives off the same vibes as the 60s/70s has me feeling extra old today lol", "timestamp": 1775347615}, {"author": "madcityboi", "author_id": "47342042007", "id": "18430307392184076", "text": "It was so different. I don't remember exactly how my friends and I made plans. I think we just showed up. 😆", "timestamp": 1775316845}, {"author": "svnmusicofficial", "author_id": "49210014084", "id": "17873505057457899", "text": "😢💯❤️", "timestamp": 1775301162}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/610798015_17859711624578440_43997740566500378_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p640x640_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMjA2eDIxNDQuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEFitruseMnTpCM2v8t1wWi_PK8TUsX5lGSfHr0Zl8S_FfLJx7pLk_TRKJmfYt_7l8&_nc_ohc=-wJEz95heqsQ7kNvwFDxCSG&_nc_gid=8s4cUd6da7TDAEmd-VSO_Q&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af3hT1Rvsjmjy_XvqRFmt_LN-K0eKporWEobyGZiXoH3bQ&oe=69D7AF91&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1137, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1137"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/610798015_17859711624578440_43997740566500378_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p750x750_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMjA2eDIxNDQuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=104&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEFitruseMnTpCM2v8t1wWi_PK8TUsX5lGSfHr0Zl8S_FfLJx7pLk_TRKJmfYt_7l8&_nc_ohc=-wJEz95heqsQ7kNvwFDxCSG&_nc_gid=8s4cUd6da7TDAEmd-VSO_Q&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0wPFI5znvLACtpuBs1XdreYu6J2BdgKazU0n9Qn0d5pQ&oe=69D7AF91&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1333, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1333"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/610798015_17859711624578440_43997740566500378_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMjA2eDIxNDQuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2Nvd